==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flying fish
<hw>Fly"ing fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A fish
which is able to leap from the water, and fly a considerable distance by
means of its large and long pectoral fins. These fishes belong to
several species of the genus <gen>Exoc⟦oe⟧tus</gen>, and are found in
the warmer parts of all the oceans.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flying fox</ent>⟦br⟧
